    Usage

    stochasim(hydist, cross_section, rv_rate = 0.1, nsim = 1000, niter = 300)

    Arguments

    hydist

    Hydrograph Distribution

    cross_section

    A "cross_section" object representing a stream's cross section.

    rv_rate

    Rate parameter for revegetation, passed to revegetate().

    nsim

    Number of event hydrographs to run; positive integer.

    niter

    Number of iterations for gbem::gbem() when running each hydrograph.

    Value

    A stochasim object, containing all the event hydrographs, and cross sections.
